oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Grand Ole Opry show at the Kiel Auditorium
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Grand ole opry (Radio program); Wagoner, Porter; Snow, Hank; Pearl, Minnie; Martha White Foods
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (red and black on white) announcing Grand Ole Opry stars Hank Snow, Porter Wagoner, Minnie Pearl, Charlie Louvin, Jim Edward Brown, Buck Trent, Tompall and the Glaser Brothers, and others at the Kiel Auditorium on January 2. Poster features advertising metal photoplates of Martha White foods.
